text: The Recap is a compilation album by rapper Mr. Envi'. It was released on January 7, 2014 by Tate Music Group, then later re-released under his own brand. ==Track listing== #Back It Off (featuring Jeramie of TRT) -- 3:00 #I'mma Boss -- 3:55 #Re Up -- 3:17 #Spotlight -- 3:00 #Where U From (featuring JB) -- 3:05 #Get At Me -- 3:25 #Don't Wait (featuring JTL) -- 3:32 #Keep It Poppin' (featuring S.G.) -- 4:16 #Do It Big (featuring S.G. & Bigg Redd) -- 4:28 ==References== == External links == * Category:2014 albums Category:Mr. Envi' albums
